        "content": "<p>If <code>cost :  Rat</code> then how to prove, for example, that <code>cost - cost / 3 = 2 * cost / 3</code>?<br>\n<code>simp</code> makes no progress. I suppose I need some lemmas from <code>Rat</code>?</p>\n<p>Similarly how to prove that <code>3 * 16 / 2 = 24</code> (where they are all <code>Rat</code>s)?</p>",
